{"tid":1354993,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工兵請入","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:38.000Z","uid":92106,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9a72ac9d45893badd2ca95726cb0872dcd7ecc","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係長期負責清拆行動嘅工程撚，有少少工業安全知識同實戰經驗想分享下。<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>工具篇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有好用嘅工具可以事半功倍，常用嘅清拆工具叫<strong>令梗</strong>，記得要買<strong>13mm</strong>個種。以下係去五金鋪買工具嘅對白：<span style=\"color: gold;\">老闆，想要個13mm棘令(勒勒令)</span>。跟住老闆就會俾下圖嘅工具你。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.gaacaang.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/F6C98848-28FF-4D77-88AD-D815F532092F.jpeg?zoom=2&amp;fit=1080%2C1080&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.gaacaang.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2FF6C98848-28FF-4D77-88AD-D815F532092F.jpeg%3Fzoom%3D2%26fit%3D1080%252C1080%26ssl%3D1&h=6ce5fe7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n價錢大概$45-$60<br />\n<br />\n有錢啲嘅買多個大力鉗/老虎鉗，唔係噉易用，有機會一齊開工再教你，或者自己google下啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大力鉗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winwincohk.com/image/cache/catalog/product-313/QJFaKphkzG-TB2_4fpceOSBuNjy0FdXXbDnVXa_!!849618390-850x1190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winwincohk.com%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct-313%2FQJFaKphkzG-TB2_4fpceOSBuNjy0FdXXbDnVXa_%21%21849618390-850x1190.jpg&h=ebdafabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">老虎鉗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.itsfun.com.tw/cacheimg/34/99/70eadc1206a90e97a3cfc90c4966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itsfun.com.tw%2Fcacheimg%2F34%2F99%2F70eadc1206a90e97a3cfc90c4966.jpg&h=101e7b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得買<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3m手套</span>，唔係好易刮損。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/3035/products/3M-LPG_grande.jpg?v=1507022168\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0703%2F3035%2Fproducts%2F3M-LPG_grande.jpg%3Fv%3D1507022168&h=ad45bbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>安全篇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈唔建議拆完一邊鏍絲之後格硬推個欄</span></span>，一黎會扭彎條鏍絲拔唔返出黎，成村人卡左係度。二黎好危險，好容易推推下成個欄跌落地。我隻腳指公就係俾人<span style=\"color: red;\">team kill</span>，痛到依家都返唔到工。第三，試過推斷鏍絲彈左出黎，危險過橡鳩子彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推欄的確可以好快，不過工具有限，相信大家都係新入行，好多時會有反效果。如果你係熟手技工，當然用返慣用嘅手法好啲，不過新仔就求下你唔好太衝動，爆腳指公真係好痛。我明白大家心急想快啲做完收工，不過欲速則不達，安全啲好。<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行動篇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一個行動小組有四種人，以下係分工安排：<br />\n<br />\n鏍絲組（兩人一組）：一人拆一邊鏍絲，要買工具同手套。<br />\n<br />\n扶欄組（二至三人一組）：係扭鏍絲期間捉實個欄，防止個欄跌落黎壓到手足。等拆唒所有鏍絲之後將個欄推向一邊放係地下。要買手套，自問大力嘅巴絲先好做，個欄都幾重。<br />\n<br />\n運輸組（三至四人一組）：將鐵欄送去工場包裝。都要買手套，要反復行好多轉，耐力同力量並重，最大力嘅巴絲先好做呢個位。<br />\n<br />\n傘兵：幫手擋下太陽防止工友曬傷。呢個post看似無用，其實極為重要，可以令工友安心工作。唔需要手套，要長傘。"},{"pid":"ba14dfb4894de1df19e76a7e24997d4c10c32d9f","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"94c2199d74d3da3bda50f9f0bdeb4eabaf8ca7f4","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"cafae93867fcc7971531af618c6f04664d6ba25d","tid":1354993,"uid":89584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b87c75ea997941a873b7ab6d5166073a3e89b80","tid":1354993,"uid":190164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b7111e66376db03a31536ba187eb5cc6d08d84","tid":1354993,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b73bf3a61b7f80979f5616b6a7b24e5f8269c26","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔想再有人買14mm令梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6861cbc1d4c3ea60ecd4afe738ddee732adfaa","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"求下大家推，唔想有人好似我噉受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98690e98dc247cd2e9d7ae70523a9aa41f990d5","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0af05f2358adc67aac53644459baef438e836bd","tid":1354993,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b73bf3a61b7f80979f5616b6a7b24e5f8269c26","tid":1354993,"uid":92106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔想再有人買14mm令梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"上環有d係14 (夢到)"},{"pid":"da690717d644aaf05ae6948c9fb9fa4f3da69f80","tid":1354993,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"點解出喺上班台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2eca4eb5bec2e8b298cc3143d0c0541a7331744","tid":1354993,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"}]}